  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Peel</strong> the potatoes and slice the spring onions finely</p>\r\n<p><strong>Remove</strong> the top<span class=\"text-danger\">(s)</span> of the courgette<span class=\"text-danger\">(s)</span></p>\r\n<p><strong>Grate</strong> the peeled potatoes and the courgette<span class=\"text-danger\">(s)</span> into a strainer</p>\r\n<p><strong>Add</strong> 2/3 of the spring onion and reserve the rest for step 8</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Place</strong> the strainer over or inside a large bowl</p>\r\n<p><strong>Tip:</strong> Ensure that the strainer rests above the bottom of the bowl so the unwanted liquid has a place to go</p>\r\n<p><strong>Sprinkle</strong> 2-3 tsp of salt over the mixture, mix well, and set aside until step 4</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, chop the beetroot into bite-size pieces</p>\r\n<p><strong>Remove</strong> the end<span class=\"text-danger\">(s)</span> of the little gem<span class=\"text-danger\">(s)</span>, then tear the little gem and mozzarella into bite-size pieces</p>\r\n<p><strong>Place</strong> the beetroot, mozzarella and little gem in a salad bowl and set aside until ready to serve</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Squeeze</strong> the excess liquid out from the potato-courgette mixture, drain, and reserve the bowl</p>\r\n<p><strong>Transfer</strong> the drained mixture into the reserved bowl and break the egg<span class=\"text-danger\">(s)</span> into the mixture</p>\r\n<p><strong>Add</strong> 30g<span class=\"text-danger\"> (60g)</span> of flour</p>\r\n<p><strong>Season</strong> to your taste with salt and pepper and mix well</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-4-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-4-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Place</strong> a wide-base pan (preferably non-stick) on a high heat and add 2-3 tbsp of vegetable oil</p>\r\n<p><strong>Once</strong> the oil is hot, drop large spoonfuls of the mixture into the pan</p>\r\n<p><strong>Spread</strong> each dollop to approx. 10cm diameter</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cook</strong> for 3 min on each side or until golden and cooked through</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-5-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-5-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Remove</strong> the fritters from the pan and place on kitchen roll on a wire rack to drain off the excess oil</p>\r\n<p><strong>Tip:</strong> Alternatively, just use kitchen roll on a plate, but don't leave them too long or else they can get soggy</p>\r\n<p><strong>Repeat</strong> the process until the whole mixture is used up</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-6-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-6-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-6-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Add</strong> the honey and mustard into a small bowl and whisk into a dressing</p>\r\n<p><strong>Season</strong> with salt and pepper to your taste</p>\r\n<p><strong>Tip:</strong> Try making the dressing by adding the ingredients into an old jam jar. Shake well to combine and serve!</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-7-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-7-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-7-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-7-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-53.-step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Drizzle</strong> the dressing over the salad and mix well</p>\r\n<p><strong>Plate</strong> the fritters, together with the salad</p>\r\n<p><strong>Garnish</strong> with the remaining spring onion and enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
